&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;It's like inviting a few thousand people on the internet to circle around you and chant "DO IT! DO IT!"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We've been talking about it in the office because last Friday (which was a slow Friday) stumbled upon a high schooler who was promising to throw a water balloon during is high school lunch if he got 10 retweets. We retweeted him, curious to see what would happen.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en"&gt;
